docs/CURRENT_STATE.md:48:- OKF/skills lifecycle.
docs/CURRENT_STATE.md:50:This is not the product highway. It is safety/evidence substrate for Agent OS. These layers should be reused only when they help a task run from intake through isolated execution, verification, aggregation, and human decision.
